                             javax.faces.component.visit.VisitCallback callback,
                             List<javax.faces.component.UIComponent> stamps)
        Visit the stamp of the trainButtonBar per row-index. The trainButtonBar will visit max two rows (for prev and next buttons), and will not visit extra rows of collection.
